@startuml field-ops-sync-lifecycle
title Field Data Sync Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Captured on Mobile (Offline)

Draft --> ReadyToSync : Submission Completed Locally
ReadyToSync --> Processing : Connection Established (Sync Initiated)

Processing --> Synced : Succesfully Transmitted to Server
Processing --> Conflict : Modification Collision detected
Processing --> Failed : Network Interruption / Schema mismatch

Synced --> Verified : Case Worker approves record
Conflict --> Draft : Manual Resolution required on Mobile

@enduml
